Tamnaḍt n '''Tarudant''' tga yat tmnaḍt ɣ [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|tsga n Sus-Massa]]. Tamaẓunt nns tga-tt [[Tarudant]].
== Tarakalt ==
Ɣ iggi n wakal n Tamnaḍt n Tarudant llan kigan n taganin, iḥudda t id:

* Ɣ iẓẓlmḍ tamnbaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Cicawa|Cicawa]] d [[Tamnaḍt n Lḥawz|Lḥawz]]
* Ɣ ugmuḍ tamnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Warzazat|Warzazat]]
* Ɣ iffus tamnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Tiznit|Tiznit]] d [[Tamnaḍt n Ṭaṭa|Ṭaṭa]]
* Ɣ tagut tamnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Actukn-Ayt Baha]], [[Tamnbaḍt n Inzggan-Ayt Mllul|Inzggan-Ayt Mllul]] d [[Tamnbaḍt n Agadir-Idawtanan|Agadir-Idawtanan]]
